608
00:26:59,630 --> 00:27:02,130
♪Forget about time♪

609
00:27:03,260 --> 00:27:07,880
♪Ignored a few missed calls♪

610
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:11,640
♪Just walk away alone♪

611
00:27:11,810 --> 00:27:16,140
♪Is this how it's like♪

612
00:27:16,480 --> 00:27:20,620
♪Couldn't find an answer♪

613
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:25,560
♪Is this how it's like♪

614
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:28,590
♪Where are you♪

615
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:32,900
(Banghe Bar)

616
00:27:40,220 --> 00:27:41,220
What are you here for?

617
00:27:41,580 --> 00:27:42,340
Why is no one here?

618
00:27:42,340 --> 00:27:44,150
Didn't you read Yong's text
in the group chat?

619
00:27:44,150 --> 00:27:45,100
It's closed today.

620
00:27:45,220 --> 00:27:46,060
Why?

621
00:27:46,160 --> 00:27:47,940
There's an orange alert for rainstorm.

622
00:27:47,940 --> 00:27:49,150
It's a once-in-a-century rain.

623
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:51,500
Really?

624
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:52,780
I have to get back to school.

625
00:27:52,780 --> 00:27:53,810
I have an exam tonight.

626
00:27:53,820 --> 00:27:54,760
You should hurry home.

627
00:27:54,760 --> 00:27:55,360
Okay, go ahead.

628
00:27:55,360 --> 00:27:56,310
I'll use the bathroom.

629
00:27:56,310 --> 00:27:58,220
I've cleaned.
Just close the doors and windows.

630
00:27:58,310 --> 00:28:00,080
- Sure, no worries.
- Turn off the power too.

631
00:28:00,080 --> 00:28:00,900
- Bye.
- Bye.

632
00:28:37,420 --> 00:28:38,260
Anyone?

633
00:28:55,740 --> 00:28:57,540
Sorry, we're closed today.

634
00:28:59,100 --> 00:29:01,460
I thought this place had a show today.

635
00:29:02,060 --> 00:29:03,180
I'm sorry.

636
00:29:07,580 --> 00:29:10,300
It's raining too hard.

637
00:29:11,940 --> 00:29:13,100
I can't leave.

638
00:29:20,420 --> 00:29:25,020
(Dong)

639
00:29:25,060 --> 00:29:25,860
Sorry,

640
00:29:25,860 --> 00:29:28,020
(Lab Building, East China Ocean University)
the phone you dialed

641
00:29:28,020 --> 00:29:29,760
is not answered for the moment,
please redial later.

642
00:29:34,140 --> 00:29:35,180
(Xiuya)

643
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:39,660
(Banghe Bar)

644
00:29:47,740 --> 00:29:48,580
Here's your drink.

645
00:29:49,500 --> 00:29:50,740
I can't leave anyway.

646
00:29:50,740 --> 00:29:52,220
Why don't you sit here for a while?

647
00:29:52,900 --> 00:29:54,260
- Thank you.
- It's fine.

648
00:30:22,900 --> 00:30:23,940
I quite like you.

649
00:30:24,900 --> 00:30:27,500
Do you want to be my girlfriend?

650
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:34,660
Can you be my girlfriend?

651
00:30:39,220 --> 00:30:40,100
Be my girlfriend?

652
00:30:46,300 --> 00:30:49,940
(Dong)

653
00:30:52,180 --> 00:30:53,020
Protein.

654
00:30:53,900 --> 00:30:54,740
17.5.

655
00:30:56,340 --> 00:30:57,180
Fat.

656
00:30:58,220 --> 00:30:59,060
3.0.

657
00:31:00,540 --> 00:31:01,740
Carbohydrate.

658
00:31:02,580 --> 00:31:03,460
1.7.

659
00:31:05,100 --> 00:31:06,340
Come, Long, take a look.

660
00:31:06,900 --> 00:31:07,740
Here.

661
00:31:15,740 --> 00:31:16,460
Xiuya,

662
00:31:16,460 --> 00:31:18,500
I called you and the bar,
but no one answered.

663
00:31:18,500 --> 00:31:19,740
Have you left already?

664
00:31:20,060 --> 00:31:20,980
(Banghe Bar)
I think

665
00:31:20,980 --> 00:31:22,660
I took the only umbrella in the bar.

666
00:31:22,660 --> 00:31:23,940
Do you still have an umbrella?

667
00:31:25,420 --> 00:31:27,390
(Yong: The bar's closed.
Why did Xiuya come?)

668
00:31:27,390 --> 00:31:29,340
(Haven't you all left?)

669
00:31:29,740 --> 00:31:30,560
Xiuya came later.

670
00:31:30,560 --> 00:31:32,220
I hurried back to school for an exam.

671
00:31:32,220 --> 00:31:33,260
So I left first.

672
00:31:33,660 --> 00:31:35,820
When I left,
I saw a customer go into Banghe Bar.

673
00:31:39,260 --> 00:31:40,900
On such a rainy day?

674
00:31:41,300 --> 00:31:42,340
Is it a man or a woman?

675
00:31:42,940 --> 00:31:43,820
A man.

676
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:51,580
The number you dialed is not answered
for the moment...

677
00:31:51,940 --> 00:31:53,460
Xiuya is not at home.

678
00:31:53,740 --> 00:31:55,500
She didn't answer my call.

679
00:31:59,060 --> 00:32:00,820
I shouldn't have left first.

680
00:32:00,820 --> 00:32:01,900
Xiuya is alone.

681
00:32:01,900 --> 00:32:03,180
What if she's in danger?

682
00:32:05,260 --> 00:32:07,420
Something's up at my bar.

683
00:32:07,420 --> 00:32:08,260
I'll go there.

684
00:32:08,780 --> 00:32:09,620
What's up?

685
00:32:11,060 --> 00:32:11,940
Do you have to go?

686
00:32:16,180 --> 00:32:17,260
Fine, I don't have to.

687
00:32:33,220 --> 00:32:34,060
Miss.

688
00:32:34,780 --> 00:32:36,060
You see, drinking alone

689
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:37,340
isn't much fun.

690
00:32:38,180 --> 00:32:42,060
Why don't you come over
and let's drink together?

691
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:43,500
To keep me company.

692
00:32:45,220 --> 00:32:47,100
I'm not good at drinking.

693
00:32:47,420 --> 00:32:48,660
Just drink a little.

694
00:32:49,220 --> 00:32:50,740
Let's chat.

695
00:32:52,780 --> 00:32:54,220
It's better than doing nothing.

696
00:33:06,220 --> 00:33:08,660
I'm at home with my wife. I can't leave.

697
00:33:08,980 --> 00:33:10,980
I'm calling a cab.
But no one picks up.

698
00:33:13,220 --> 00:33:14,100
Don't worry about it.

699
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:14,980
I'm not far away.

700
00:33:14,980 --> 00:33:15,820
I'll take a look.

701
00:33:22,900 --> 00:33:24,420
I'll pass by Banghe Bar anyway.

702
00:33:58,280 --> 00:33:59,580
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

703
00:34:03,660 --> 00:34:05,540
You said you're here
for stand-up comedy.

704
00:34:05,940 --> 00:34:06,780
Yes.

705
00:34:07,180 --> 00:34:09,420
I thought this place had a show tonight.

706
00:34:09,580 --> 00:34:11,060
Turns out I came here for nothing.

707
00:34:11,940 --> 00:34:13,820
Actually, I'm a stand-up comedian.

708
00:34:14,020 --> 00:34:15,060
I came here today

709
00:34:15,060 --> 00:34:16,420
because I want to try my new jokes.

710
00:34:16,420 --> 00:34:17,820
But there's no audience.

711
00:34:19,220 --> 00:34:20,620
If you want to listen,

712
00:34:20,620 --> 00:34:22,140
I can perform it.

713
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:23,500
- Really?
- Sure.

714
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:24,980
- Okay.
- Fine.

715
00:34:28,160 --> 00:34:30,580
This is my first time performing
before just one person.

716
00:34:31,860 --> 00:34:33,460
If you find it funny,

717
00:34:33,460 --> 00:34:35,100
laugh out loud.

718
00:34:35,100 --> 00:34:36,380
If you don't find it funny,

719
00:34:37,540 --> 00:34:39,380
you can't run out in this rain anyway.

720
00:35:20,620 --> 00:35:21,460
Sir.

721
00:35:51,900 --> 00:35:53,460
I've met a very strange group

722
00:35:53,460 --> 00:35:55,500
of audiences before.

723
00:35:55,900 --> 00:35:57,220
When I interacted with them,

724
00:35:57,220 --> 00:35:58,500
they ignored me.

725
00:35:58,820 --> 00:36:01,500
I asked them if
they'd seen stand-up comedy before.

726
00:36:02,540 --> 00:36:04,140
They were all silent.

727
00:36:04,220 --> 00:36:05,140
Ever since then,

728
00:36:05,140 --> 00:36:07,820
I've invented a new way
of doing stand-up comedy.

729
00:36:07,980 --> 00:36:10,500
It's called classroom stand-up comedy.

730
00:36:10,560 --> 00:36:12,460
Whenever I meet
an uncooperative audience again,

731
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:13,580
I still ask

732
00:36:13,980 --> 00:36:15,580
if they've seen stand-up comedy before.

733
00:36:16,860 --> 00:36:18,140
No one answers, right?

734
00:36:18,860 --> 00:36:20,220
Then I'll call the roll.

735
00:36:20,620 --> 00:36:21,580
This classmate.

736
00:36:22,140 --> 00:36:23,020
Answer me, please.

737
00:36:23,020 --> 00:36:24,450
Have you seen stand-up comedy before?

738
00:36:25,020 --> 00:36:26,500
- Yes.
- Yes?

739
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:28,180
If it's yes, why didn't you answer me?

740
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:30,160
Did you watch shows for me?

741
00:36:30,160 --> 00:36:31,640
I'm standing here. Are people laughing

742
00:36:31,640 --> 00:36:32,620
for me or for you?

743
00:36:32,980 --> 00:36:33,860
When I was little,

744
00:36:33,860 --> 00:36:36,380
I thought there were the two weirdest things
teachers would say:

745
00:36:36,700 --> 00:36:38,220
I see what you're doing

746
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:39,620
in the classroom very clearly.

747
00:36:39,620 --> 00:36:41,060
I just don't want to mind it.

748
00:36:44,580 --> 00:36:45,500
(On this rainy night,)

749
00:36:45,560 --> 00:36:48,150
(with only one audience,
Xiuya put on a brilliant performance.)

750
00:36:48,260 --> 00:36:49,120
(But she didn't know,)

751
00:36:49,120 --> 00:36:51,580
(she was also a sight to behold.)

752
00:36:54,100 --> 00:36:55,160
There's another thing:

753
00:36:55,160 --> 00:36:57,150
If you don't have your homework,
you didn't do it.

754
00:36:57,460 --> 00:36:59,140
It's the same as the last one.

755
00:36:59,140 --> 00:37:01,020
(Shi Ye: I found her.)
It makes no sense.

756
00:37:01,020 --> 00:37:02,700
(She's at Banghe Bar.)
What does it mean?

757
00:37:02,900 --> 00:37:05,580
Not having homework is
different from not doing it.

758
00:37:05,940 --> 00:37:07,180
Thank you, I'm Xiuya.

759
00:37:09,140 --> 00:37:09,980
Great.

760
00:37:10,980 --> 00:37:11,820
Shi Ye?

761
00:37:12,820 --> 00:37:13,700
Why are you here?

762
00:37:14,760 --> 00:37:16,700
I left something behind
and came back for it.

763
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:19,660
We ran out of umbrellas at the bar.

764
00:37:19,660 --> 00:37:20,940
We're trapped here.

765
00:37:21,860 --> 00:37:23,020
I'll lend you my raincoat.

766
00:37:25,500 --> 00:37:26,460
Thank you.

767
00:37:26,460 --> 00:37:27,980
I'll pay for the drinks.

768
00:37:27,980 --> 00:37:28,820
Don't bother.

769
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:30,700
You helped me try out
the new jokes today.

770
00:37:30,700 --> 00:37:31,820
It's on me.

771
00:37:33,020 --> 00:37:34,340
That's too generous.

772
00:37:34,620 --> 00:37:35,460
Thank you.

773
00:37:38,820 --> 00:37:39,820
- Bye.
- Bye.

774
00:37:41,660 --> 00:37:43,140
Why didn't you pick up your phone?

775
00:37:44,820 --> 00:37:46,700
I left my phone in the office.

776
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:50,620
It's just the two of you here.

777
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:52,500
Aren't you scared?

778
00:37:52,700 --> 00:37:53,940
What should I be scared of?

779
00:37:54,020 --> 00:37:56,020
It's a bar with bright lights.

780
00:37:56,020 --> 00:37:57,300
What can he do to me?

781
00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:03,500
Why is the power out?

782
00:38:04,140 --> 00:38:10,300
(Banghe Bar)

783
00:38:11,020 --> 00:38:12,580
The fuse is fine.

784
00:38:15,150 --> 00:38:16,020
Found it.

785
00:38:16,160 --> 00:38:17,280
You found out what's wrong?

786
00:38:18,940 --> 00:38:20,140
I found Yong's wine.

787
00:38:20,140 --> 00:38:21,300
He said this is good.

788
00:38:21,300 --> 00:38:22,860
It's for special occasions.

789
00:38:24,010 --> 00:38:26,020
What's today's special occasion?

790
00:38:26,160 --> 00:38:27,860
Today has the once-in-a-century rain.

791
00:38:27,900 --> 00:38:28,740
Isn't this special?

792
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:31,020
So what are we celebrating

793
00:38:31,020 --> 00:38:32,020
on this special day?

794
00:38:33,020 --> 00:38:36,020
We're celebrating that
you gave a brilliant performance

795
00:38:36,140 --> 00:38:37,620
under such extreme conditions.

796
00:38:38,700 --> 00:38:39,540
Thank you.

797
00:38:56,020 --> 00:38:57,500
Actually, I'm still worried about

798
00:38:57,500 --> 00:38:59,020
the performance at Alpaca.

799
00:38:59,540 --> 00:39:01,300
Only you have performed there before.

800
00:39:01,300 --> 00:39:02,340
What was it like?

801
00:39:04,330 --> 00:39:05,170
Thank you.

802
00:39:05,820 --> 00:39:07,140
You take it too seriously.

803
00:39:07,140 --> 00:39:08,500
Think about what an alpaca is.

804
00:39:09,300 --> 00:39:10,140
An animal.

805
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:13,020
That kind of animal.

806
00:39:19,700 --> 00:39:20,540
Think about it.

807
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:21,980
A club

808
00:39:22,540 --> 00:39:24,980
named after that kind of animal.

809
00:39:24,980 --> 00:39:26,140
How serious can it be?

810
00:39:26,160 --> 00:39:28,560
They were a bunch of unserious people

811
00:39:28,560 --> 00:39:30,150
trying to rebel against the authority.

812
00:39:30,500 --> 00:39:33,420
A bunch of unorthodox people
gather together

813
00:39:33,430 --> 00:39:35,300
to study how to break the rules.

814
00:39:35,700 --> 00:39:37,300
After a while,

815
00:39:37,300 --> 00:39:39,380
the rule-breakers set new rules.

816
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:41,540
The rebels became the new authority.

817
00:39:41,620 --> 00:39:44,100
The dragon slayer
became the evil dragon.

818
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:45,620
That's the most hilarious part.

819
00:39:46,700 --> 00:39:48,460
I understand what you mean.

820
00:39:48,500 --> 00:39:50,700
You want me not to take them seriously.

821
00:39:50,700 --> 00:39:52,340
If you take them too seriously,

822
00:39:52,340 --> 00:39:54,500
you'll feel that their comments
to you are correct.

823
00:39:54,980 --> 00:39:56,940
Don't ever let others tell you
what's right.

824
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:58,620
That's not stand-up comedy.

825
00:40:00,860 --> 00:40:02,620
In light of the spirit
of stand-up comedy,

826
00:40:02,620 --> 00:40:03,900
I shouldn't take

827
00:40:03,900 --> 00:40:05,500
what you just told me seriously.

828
00:40:06,100 --> 00:40:08,340
In light of the spirit
of stand-up comedy,

829
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:09,260
if I tell you

830
00:40:09,260 --> 00:40:10,500
that you shouldn't listen to me,

831
00:40:10,500 --> 00:40:12,420
then you shouldn't
take my words seriously.

832
00:40:12,500 --> 00:40:13,660
So you have to listen to me.

833
00:40:15,700 --> 00:40:17,180
Let me think about it.

834
00:40:28,900 --> 00:40:29,940
Amazing sunset.

835
00:40:30,160 --> 00:40:32,580
Hold on. How can there be a sunset
when it rains so heavily?

836
00:40:32,980 --> 00:40:34,980
It must be reflections.

837
00:40:35,700 --> 00:40:37,020
Where does the water come from?

838
00:40:38,580 --> 00:40:40,100
Oops. The bar is flooded.

839
00:40:47,490 --> 00:40:48,420
Take some rest. I'll do.

840
00:40:48,420 --> 00:40:49,260
It's fine.

841
00:41:00,860 --> 00:41:01,700
